            "formula": "\\left(\\frac{1}{x}\\right)' = -\\frac{1}{x^2}\n(x^{-n})' = -n x^{-n-1} = -\\frac{n}{x^{n+1}}\n\\frac{\\frac{1}{x+h} - \\frac{1}{x}}{h} = \\frac{-1}{x(x+h)} \\xrightarrow{h \\to 0} -\\frac{1}{x^2}",
